node.text:
Fanatic Bolsonaro supporters are burning my books because I said that they need to feed the Brazilians before exporting food (people without regular access to BASIC food in Brazil reached 10.3 million. In 2013, it was 7.2 million (IBGE).
There are other videos like this, but I had to choose one
This reminds me of May 10, 1933, when nazis burned books of writers that were against Hitler
